<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/353312-why-does-george-mouse-laugh-at-the-name-of">Why does George Mouse laugh at the name of &quot;The Noisy Bridge Rod and Gun Club&quot;? Is this some pun I don&#39;t get?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_353312'><a id="like_count_community_question_353312" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/353312?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F90619.Little_Big">like</a></span>

